citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:55 pm on 4
January 2022.
Called on cell phone x2, honked, knocked on cattery door, drove around farm buildings looking for people. Left ~3:40 pm
after placing leave-behind flyer on cattery door.
End Section
